---

<section
  class="flex flex-col gap-2 bg-neutral-800 mx-auto rounded-md overflow-hidden text-white justify-center"
>
  <h1
    class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-purple-600 p-4 rounded-t-md"
  >
    Connect
